<item>
 <title>Rhino Bamboo Industry Felicitated</title>
 <link>http://www.necbdc.org.in/article/rhino-bamboo-industry-felicitated</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-content-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.necbdc.org.in/sites/default/files/article/National%20Award%20%20Small%20%26%20Medium%20Scale%20Industries%20of%20the%20country%20%282009-10%29.jpg&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;373&quot; alt=&quot;National Award for Best Enterprise amongst the Small &amp;amp; Medium Scale Industries of the country (2009-10)&quot; title=&quot;National Award for Best Enterprise amongst the Small &amp;amp; Medium Scale Industries of the country (2009-10)&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Guwahati based Rhino Bamboo Industry, the only one of its kind in the entire country manufacturing mechanized bamboo products like blinds, handicrafts items etc. was conferred the National Award for Best Enterprise amongst the Small &amp;amp; Medium Scale Industries of the country (2009-10). At a function held in New Delhi on 28th August 2009, the award was received by the proprietor of the enterprise Mr. Rajiv Goswami. He was also awarded by the Ministry of DoNER during the NE Business Summit 2010 held at Kolkata as one of the best performing enterprise from the North East.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/cb-january-2010&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;C&amp;amp;B January 2010&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
