<item>
 <title>French Designers at CBTC</title>
 <link>http://www.necbdc.org.in/article/french-designers-cbtc-0</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Two designer, Mr. Wilfrid and Ms. Marie Le Gac visited CBTC during the month of November, 2009 as part of their project on design building through collaboration between designers and craftsmen in an eco-friendly way. During their month-long stay in Guwahati, they &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;exchanged their experiences, knowhow and expertise with the CBTC Trainers &amp;amp; Craftsmen in the field of creating bamboo based furniture and kitchenware using bamboo as the main material.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;Style1&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; line-height: 13.8pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/cb-january-2010&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;C&amp;amp;B January 2010&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
