<item>
 <title>Consultative Meets on Agarbatti stick</title>
 <link>http://www.necbdc.org.in/article/consultative-meets-agarbatti-stick</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-content-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.necbdc.org.in/sites/default/files/article/Consultative%20Meets%20on%20Agarbatti%20stick.jpg&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;369&quot; alt=&quot;Consultative Meets on Agarbatti stick&quot; title=&quot;Consultative Meets on Agarbatti stick&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;A consultative meet was organized by CBTC in collaboration with ITC Agarbatti Division at the AIDC Conference Hall, Guwahati on 8th December 2009.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The main purpose of the meeting was to have a brainstorming exercise for the development of the agarbatti supply chain in the region. It is deduced that 70% to 80% of the stick used by the nation&#039;s agarbatti industry comes from North East region alone and the estimated market turnover is to the tune of Rs 1900 Crore growing @ 10% every year, providing livelihood to over 5 million people. The local players are dominating over 80% of the value as of now. The volume of ITC requirement is approximately 50 metric tonnes per month.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Besides the CBTC officials and Shri VM Rajsekharan, CEO, ITC and Shri C Srinivasan, Operations Manager, ITC Agarbatti Division, the meeting was attended by official delegatesfrom UNIDO,AIDC, and different state government organizations and other enterprises.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/cb-january-2010&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;C&amp;amp;B January 2010&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
 <pubDate>Fri, 01 Jan 2010 09:27:59 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>CBTC Staff</dc:creator>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">66 at http://www.necbdc.org.in</guid>
