<item>
 <title>Training on &quot;Bamboo Charcoal Making&quot;</title>
 <link>http://www.necbdc.org.in/article/training-bamboo-charcoal-making</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-content-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.necbdc.org.in/sites/default/files/article/Bamboo%20Charcoal%20Making%202.jpg&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;463&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;A total of 38 persons attended CBTC&#039;s training programme on Bamboo Charcoal Making. Held &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;from 16th to 21st November 2009 at the NagaIan Bamboo Resource Centre in Dimapur, Nagaland, th programme was mainly based on practical aspects o utilization of Bamboo and manufacturing of Bambc Charcoal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
