<item>
 <title>Jupuri Ghar,  Kaziranga, Assam</title>
 <link>http://www.necbdc.org.in/article/jupuri-ghar-kaziranga-assam</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-content-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.necbdc.org.in/sites/default/files/article/jupuri%20ghat.jpg&quot; width=&quot;777&quot; height=&quot;338&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;This project is unique in its construction as it is the first time a Bamboo frame has been combined with Bamboo mat boards for a structure. The Plinth was already made with concrete bythe Tourism Department when the CBTC was approached to take up the project. The construction was planned with the Bamboo poles combined with Mat board panel for walls. This unique way of making such structure helped in reducing the Cost and the time taken for completion. As a large number of cottages had to be made ready before the impending tourist season, this method of construction helped in maintaining the time line and also gave a unique look to the structure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Year of Construction - 2008&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost of Project - Rs. 2.50 lakhs per cottage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Time taken for completion - 180 days (for 8 cottages)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The project was initiated by the Tourism Department for tourist lodge in the world famous wild life sanctuary of Kaziranga, Assam.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/cb-january-2010&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;C&amp;amp;B January 2010&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
