<item>
 <title>A college cafeteria at Handique Girls College </title>
 <link>http://www.necbdc.org.in/article/college-cafeteria-handique-girls-college</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-content-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;http://www.necbdc.org.in/sites/default/files/article/Cafeteria%20at%20handique%20college.jpg&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;374&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;A college cafeteria for one of the oldest intuition of the region was conceived as a partially covered space that would cater to the students needs and also a place for small gatherings. The structure was made with a Bamboo columns and a large span truss over the &lt;/span&gt;space. There was also a lot of provision for fixing glass as the area needed to be well ventilated and &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;bright.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;The construction gave a lot of exposure to the students studying in the institute. The project was jointly funded by the Handique College and CBTC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Year of Construction — 2009&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cost of Completion — Rs. 3.5 lakhs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Time of Completeion — 120 days.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-tags field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tags/cb-january-2010&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;C&amp;amp;B January 2010&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
