&lt;h3&gt;Training&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CBTC conducts training programmes on a regular basis. A training manual has been developed and &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.008px;&quot;&gt;made available for bamboo housing constructions. CBTC has collaborated with various institutions such as IPRITI, BMPTC, TIMPACK, INBAR and UNIDO for technical support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
